# Outreach Cadence

Document the repeatable rhythm that generates pipeline conversations.

| Element | Decision |
|---------|----------|
| **Primary outreach channel** | LinkedIn DMs / email / communities / referrals / cold call |
| **Weekly volume** | e.g., 10 warm LinkedIn messages, 2 community answers, 1 referral ask |
| **Days / times** | e.g., Tue–Thu 9–11 AM local |
| **Message length** | e.g., 2–3 sentences, one specific hook |
| **Follow-up rule** | e.g., 1 polite follow-up after 5 business days; then move on |
| **CRM / tracker update** | After every touch, update `.work.biz/pipeline/pipeline_tracker.md` |
| **Owner** | Who does this work each week |

## Weekly checklist

- [ ] Outreach volume target met
- [ ] Follow-ups sent
- [ ] New conversations logged in pipeline tracker
- [ ] One piece of content published or engaged with

## Notes

Use this space to record what is working, what is not, and adjustments to test.
